00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:04.560
Wenchang, if you speak louder,

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:06.230
Father can still hear you

00:02:06.430 --> 00:02:07.480
even if he isn't at home.

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:14.680
Stand up.

