00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:53.390
Am I not good enough?

00:04:55.390 --> 00:04:56.230
I understand.

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:58.600
Wenchang may be playful,

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:00.240
