00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.430
but took the imperial exams and went

00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:16.070
to the Court of Judicial Review.

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:19.120
Shilan,

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:22.430
